---
title: Baked Pumpkin & Sage Brown Butter Risotto with Parmesan & Pine Nuts
description: This rich, creamy risotto comes together in the oven, leaving you free to create a quick and flavourful sage brown butter to stir through at the end. This easy addition takes this vegetarian meal to the next level – taste it and see!

*Unfortunately, this week's green beans were in short supply, so we've replaced them with sweetcorn. Don't worry, the recipe will be just as delicious!*
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/baked-pumpkin-risotto-9c80e7d8.jpg
